  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I can take it in Spanish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I went there and we got the license right away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And a few days later, he took me and-- he-- in a few words, he told me you have to take me in 22 hours at [?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mulerbach ?] Hotel in Kansas City, Missouri.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said-- in my way, I said, go [NON-ENGLISH], you know, in the back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I take a card-- you know, a map.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And here I'm there in 22 hours, I took him to the [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Mulerbach ?] Hotel in Kansas City, Missouri.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I stay there for a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And first he told me that no, this is too expensive here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to go across the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I says, yeah, I'll go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was paying me well, at that time giving me $125 a week, you know-- good money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I-- I said, OK, then I'll come and help you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the only thing, I was smiling and showing the dresses to all these old ladies from Pasadena, you know, from around Missouri there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, I was-- I was good in this work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I knew enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I smile.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was writing orders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This, And he said to me, you know, move to me-- with me at [LAUGHS] the Mulerbach Hotel as my-- then the Missouri-- the Kansas River was flooding up, you know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said to me, I can't use you anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I called New York, a friend of mine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went to New York.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From then, a friend of mine from California-- we were traveling together, coming to this country, to the USA-- by the name of Nico Minardos.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was studying motion picture directing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was nine years younger than I was.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
